Comment: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:23.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:27.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「proof！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「それが　二つ　結ぶ絆だから」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「my dream！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「明日の扉の向こう期待しちゃう」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:38.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「alone！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:44.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もしも月のない　空に星が輝いても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「no magic！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,もしも太陽が無い　空の雲が流れてても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,淋しそうに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.78,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,当たり前に　隣に居た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:01.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,君を探してる二人映る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,『frame Decorate』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,思うがままワガまま　ありのままに並べよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,相性『Plus＋ Minus－ Multiply× Divide÷ 』by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:10.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,全部好き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Calling me Calling you (and you)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,君と歩きたい未来階段（stairs）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Lucky Lucky Shiny 二人の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ときめきDreamin'　明日晴れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,なら　万事オーライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっとブルー　Weakness「but happy」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,けど君が居るから　Being saved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,無駄な時間なんて無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,雨上がる空をWaiting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Check it out　見上げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Courage is in two worlds\Nそう Together now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「proof！」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:46.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「それが　二つ　結ぶ絆だから」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:49.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,Everyone smiles at the beautiful girls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,「どんな明日を照らすのかな？ スポットライト」
Comment: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.53,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,勇氣兩個世界都在\N所以是時候一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:27.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「證據」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「就是緊繫你我的羈絆」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,每個人都對漂亮的少女微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.83,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「我的夢想」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:37.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「不禁期待明天之後會是怎樣」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:38.38,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「一人」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:44.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,縱使月色淡去 繁星也能閃耀夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「無關魔法」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:51.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,即便太陽不在 雲朵也湍流在天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,與寂寞陪伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.78,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,理所當然地 守護在彼此身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:01.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,尋找你的身音 把兩人倒映
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,盛裝點綴於畫框
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,隨心所欲 撒嬌任性 就這原原本本地並列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:10.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,契合度是「加減乘除」的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:10.99,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,全都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,呼喚感召你與我（你也一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,想和你一同登上未來的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,幸運有趣陽光的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,怦然心動的夢境 明日肯定天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.01,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,如此萬事都行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:28.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,情緒微藍 稍怕懦弱「但很幸福」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:32.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,因有你在得到了救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,絕沒有時間被虛度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.98,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,不過等候雨過天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:39.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,抬起頭 快來看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:42.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,勇氣兩個世界都在\N所以是時候一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「證據」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:46.65,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「就是緊繫你我的羈絆」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:49.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,每個人都對漂亮的少女微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.19,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,「聚光燈下 映照的明天又能怎樣」
Comment: 1,0:00:16.25,0:00:19.25,main-JP,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.50,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,合宿やるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.29,main-JP,All,0,0,0,,合宿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.88,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,この間のクイズ　あれで痛感したのよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.88,0:00:31.72,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,今の私たちにはチームワークが足りないって
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.72,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,だから　合宿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.81,0:00:37.06,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,暑いのにどうでしたくない
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.94,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,これも仕事よ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.94,0:00:42.65,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,歌唱とダンスを鍛えつつ　お互いのことを知る
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.65,0:00:45.94,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ついでにオフっぽい動画とかあげられたら最高
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.44,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,バーベキューもやるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.24,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,はい　行きたいです
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.82,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いい返事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.28,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,せなも行くよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.58,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.58,0:00:55.79,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃんは
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.33,0:00:57.83,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,えっと
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.38,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,行こうよ　ルルちゃんともっと話したいな
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.13,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,それじゃあ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.51,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,よーし決まり　合宿で
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.51,0:01:12.05,main-JP,All,0,0,0,,お
Comment: 1,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.94,main-JP,,0,0,0,,main
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.24,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.45,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あずき
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.03,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,泊まりで出かけるなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.70,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お母さん達になんて言えばいいと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.95,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,そうねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.87,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,言い訳　言い訳
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.13,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,正直に話しちゃおうか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.21,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,ダメよ　魔法のことは誰にも秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.22,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,友達に手伝ってもらうとか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.68,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,友達なんて　いないから
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.02,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,私は友達だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.65,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいす　これどうやって渡せばいいと思う
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.11,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,普通に渡せば
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.82,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,普通ってどんな　教えてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.53,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.87,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,それより合宿
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.50,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あっ　合宿
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.79,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,言い訳 言い訳
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.67,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.59,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リッド
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.30,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.97,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いろいろいい感じに合宿行かせて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.14,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.57,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,頼んだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.91,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,じゃあ　お姉ちゃんにプレゼント作戦のお会議を再開します
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.62,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ええ　やだやだ　眠いよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.83,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,準備できた
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.92,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,うん　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.04,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,あ　よかった
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.75,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,ああ　風
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.88,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.17,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,えっ　急にすまん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.01,0:04:39.18,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,父さんたちこれから出かけなきゃいけないんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.05,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.72,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,茉莉ちゃんとうちの店で
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.97,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,少し遠くのマルシェに参加することになったの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.35,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,遠くって　どこ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.35,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}どこやったかな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.10,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,ん　どこだっけ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.23,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,確か　西だよ　西
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.78,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,迎えに来たよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.20,main-JP,Mari,0,0,0,,流　風　お母さんたち借りてくね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.99,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,今行くね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.29,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,とにかく西だ　明後日の夜までには帰るから
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.75,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ええ　明後日
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.75,0:05:18.01,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの　私も出かける予定があるんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.92,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　お姉ちゃんも
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.68,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,風も
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.51,main-JP,Mom,0,0,0,,戸締りよろしくね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.09,main-JP,Dad,0,0,0,,{\an8}西　西　西
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,魔法　すごっ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.35,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,うまくいったな
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,準備オッケーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.04,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.42,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　あのね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.30,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.59,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,この前見かけて可愛かったから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.80,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんにも一個あげる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.01,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.81,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,二個セットだったの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.60,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.81,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いい匂い
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.19,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,大事に使うね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,渡しちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.04,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.83,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,パムパムパワー
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.43,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今日も可愛いね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.73,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう出たー
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.03,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,きた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.49,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,こっちこっち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.16,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お待たせ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.20,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,きげんいいな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.50,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そんなに楽しみだったの
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.59,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ドレにする
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.43,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えーまた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.68,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,次　ルル
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.10,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.93,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ほ　はい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.06,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.52,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あかりです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.53,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あっねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.48,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,次私ね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.36,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,うん　悪いねあかり
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.49,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,顔に出すぎ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.91,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,今度クソ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.29,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,いっつもいるよね君たち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.13,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,ここ電車なんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.88,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,欲しいの
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.21,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.18,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.81,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,へー
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.19,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,思ってたよりいいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.32,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,大きいですね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,広い
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.07,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,中もきれい
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.03,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,私奥見てくる
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.33,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,かくれんぼできちゃいそう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.43,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,うん　いいね　練習に使えそう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.72,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,戻ってきた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.64,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,よく借りるだねこんな立派なの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.90,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.78,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,それがさ　結構安かったの　ね社長
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.03,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,プライベートビーチ付きで
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.78,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,この辺りの相場の半分以下
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.49,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,もともと売りに出していたらしいが
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.49,0:09:18.16,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,結局売れず自前で貸し出しているようだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.79,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,まあ　掘り出しもんだわな
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.58,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,俺は別の宿にいるから
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.13,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,あとよろしく
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.00,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,ご近所さんに迷惑かけるなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.96,main-JP,All,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.34,0:09:30.97,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,まっ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.10,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,周りはなんもないけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.10,0:09:39.43,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,えっと　それで合宿って何からすれば
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.77,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え　探検でしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.52,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,部屋決めからじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.77,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そんなのあと まずは
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.53,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,泳ぐよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.07,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,水着どうして
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.20,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,事務所から持ってきたんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,泳いでもいいの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.37,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そ　そうですよ　練習しに来たのに
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.83,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,え　夏で　海でプライベートビーチだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.63,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,泳ぐしかないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.88,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,泳ぐか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.88,0:10:09.76,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.17,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やったー
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.13,0:10:12.55,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ずる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.18,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ほら　ルルも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.68,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,えへへ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.71,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うちも賑やかになったね
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.38,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,最初は二人だけだったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.34,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,社長もいたじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.97,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そうだった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.10,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,でもいい子たちが入ってきてくれてラッキー
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.89,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ねえ　このまま行ったら
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.15,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,芸能界制覇できるんじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.15,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どうかな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.11,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,ヨイショ　ヨイショ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.37,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,次　リップロール
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.37,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ため息つくみたいに　もう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.59,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,次　フミング
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.72,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,もう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.48,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,遊んだ後なのに
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.73,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,なんであんなに踊れるんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.69,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,本気だからだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.11,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,アイドルに必要なことは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.28,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,全部全力でやるんだ　塔子は
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.54,0:12:06.21,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,塔子さん　すごいんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.96,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ルルもリリーも
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.00,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,今のステップを覚えるのが今日のノルマね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.17,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.05,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,で　できるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.30,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,やるな　世奈なんかアドバイスない
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.35,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,まぁ　300回もやれば覚えられるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.52,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,300
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.39,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,覚えられるまで夕飯ないからね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.60,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,アイドルって大変
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.32,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,がん　頑張りましょう　リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.20,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,これ二人に持っていって
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.20,0:12:40.99,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.58,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.84,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,もう無理
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,動けない　うわ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.01,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,繰り返してればそのうち慣れるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.30,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あっ　カバッピー
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.68,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,少し休もっか
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.26,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.77,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっと
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.56,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そういえば　塔子さんと世奈さんって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いつからアイドルやってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.65,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,去年の春　いきなり塔子が言い出したの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.15,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,へぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.28,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,いろいろやってたんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.33,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なかなかうまくいかなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.91,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,そしたら二人が来た
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.33,0:13:26.99,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.54,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子もはしゃいでるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.42,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,二人となら夢が叶うかもって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.38,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,夢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.92,0:13:34.79,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.59,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,アイドルで成功して　みんなを驚かせること
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.17,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,それが塔子の夢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.05,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,そのためだけに会社まで起こして
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.35,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,昔からやることが大胆なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.93,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,二人ってすっごい仲良し
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.60,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ただの友達だって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.06,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,写真見せて　昔の
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.77,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,やだよ　恥ずかしい
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.94,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,飲み物持ってきました
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.99,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.99,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8}見たい見たい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.36,0:14:04.49,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あと　私も見たいです　写真
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.33,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,えぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.91,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みーせて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.96,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,元気ありやまってるな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.38,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,はい　休憩終わり
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.46,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,さっきのとこ復讐やるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.77,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,撮れてるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.18,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,配信って何を話せば
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.85,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,緊張する
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.81,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あ　人入ってきた
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.65,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,こんばんは　プロダクションわんすもあです
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.24,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,初めてみんなで動画回してます
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.82,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,はいみんな挨拶
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.45,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どうも　世奈です
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.20,main-JP,Lilly,0,0,0,,こんばんは　リリィです
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.70,main-JP,Lulu,0,0,0,,ルルル　ルルです
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.33,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルルル
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.96,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,気合入りすぎ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.04,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そういうわけじゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.38,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,最後に塔子です
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.71,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　コメント来てる
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.17,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,何処だって
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.38,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,合宿用のコテージです
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.72,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,イエーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.68,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,イエーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.60,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,イ　イエーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.22,0:15:13.77,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,えっと　なんか話題ある
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.94,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,話題　話題
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.40,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃんある
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.65,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,話題　ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.41,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,イエーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.37,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,イエーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.32,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,イエーイ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.33,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,みんなカメラ回るまでいっぱい喋ってたのに
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.29,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.04,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あ　どんどん人入ってくれてる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.01,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,こんばんは
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.88,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,コメント来てる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.13,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,地獄クイズ見ました
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　結構見てくれた人多いみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ファンになりました　だって
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.93,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.94,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あ　ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.02,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,計算通り
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ファンが増えればこっちのものよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.32,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}リリィちゃん好き
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.28,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あ　リリィさん好きだって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.91,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.87,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,リリィちゃんファンです
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.99,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,わあ　いっぱい来た
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.99,0:16:16.12,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いいねいいね　質問ある人は投げてって
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.71,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}困ってるリリィちゃんか　かわいいいい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.75,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}推してるものありますか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.75,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,待って早い
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.75,0:16:21.67,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}私はリリィちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.92,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}尊敬するアイドルとかいる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.92,0:16:23.96,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}私はリリィちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.63,main-JP,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}リリィちゃんお休みの日はなにしてるの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.55,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ああもう　言い切れないってば
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.88,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,また　ゆっくり　ゆっくりお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.64,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.68,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,みんなすごーい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.27,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,あ　またコメント来た　やった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.65,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,疲れたけど楽しかった
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.94,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,視聴者数も3000個いると
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.03,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,全然対応できないもんだね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.45,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,びっくりしたわ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.95,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,二人だけの時はここまで反響なかったのにね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.12,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィとルルのおかげかな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.45,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.83,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,本気で言ってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.83,0:17:03.13,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,二人ともうちに来てくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.47,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,でも　私も負けないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.68,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,さぁ明日もグンガン練習するよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.14,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,今日はもう就寝
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.30,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,グンガン
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.51,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,はあ　盛り上がっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.35,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お手柔らかにお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.49,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,トイレ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.60,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,一人で行けたでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.14,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,だって　怖いもん
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,どこから来たの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.62,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,どこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.29,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,待ってよー　えー
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.87,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あずき
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.16,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,うぐいすのところかな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.00,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.96,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,おはよう　眠れた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.96,0:19:08.75,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.01,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.88,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,あとはリリィだけだね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.88,0:19:19.85,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あの子　絶対朝起きられないタイプだと思ってたよ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.85,0:19:20.89,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,だね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.10,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私　お越しに行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.36,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.99,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,おはようございます
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.99,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,朝ですよー
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.25,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いない
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.58,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あずき達も
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.79,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いない
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.42,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい　他の部屋も探してみたんですけど
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.42,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,どこにもいないみたいで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.93,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィ　どこ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.93,0:19:58.64,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.18,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,外に出たのかな　海とか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.44,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,あ　あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.06,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,塔子さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ドアが開かない　鍵かかってないのに
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.45,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,え　寝ぼけてるの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.95,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ほんとだって　やってみてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.41,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,開かない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.95,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,他に出入り口あったよね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.96,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,こっちも
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.00,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,窓も
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.46,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.09,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なんだよこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.55,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,と　塔子さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.47,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,社長に電話してみる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.06,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.60,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,社長　緊急事態
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.85,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィがいなくなっちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.23,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,散歩でも行ってんじゃないのか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.44,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そうじゃないんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.74,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,私たちも外に出られなくなって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.62,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,おい　声…ルカ　おい
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.87,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.87,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,テレビの音は消してくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.87,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,えぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.21,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,笑い声
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.38,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,とにかく変な声がうるさくて聞こえないんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.59,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,テレビ…ついて何…何言ってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.68,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,え　あ　あの　塔子
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.43,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,社長　社長
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.94,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.82,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,電波が
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.82,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.66,0:21:44.57,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.97,0:22:01.30,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,何なの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.49,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何が起きてるの
Comment: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:19.25,main-CN,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.50,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,來合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.29,main-CN,All,0,0,0,,合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:27.88,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,上次的問答 讓我痛感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:31.72,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,現在的我們沒一點團隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:33.72,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,所以我們要合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:37.06,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,天氣很熱什麼都不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.94,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,這也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:42.65,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,一邊鍛鍊唱歌跳舞 一邊互相了解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:45.94,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,順便拍些私密影片就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.44,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,還會舉辦燒烤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.24,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好耶 我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.82,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,回答很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.28,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,世奈也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.58,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:55.79,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,露露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:57.83,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.38,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,一起來吧 我想和露露說更多話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.13,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那麼就這麼定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.51,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,好 決定啦 合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:12.05,main-CN,All,0,0,0,,好耶
Comment: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.94,main-CN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.24,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.45,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,紅豆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.03,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,外出並且在外面過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.70,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,要怎麼和爸爸媽媽說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.95,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.87,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,理由 理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.13,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,要不直接實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.21,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,不行 魔法對任何人都要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.22,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,說是去幫朋友忙怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.68,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,朋友什麼的 我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.02,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,我可是你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.65,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆 這個要怎麼樣送給她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.11,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,正常送給她囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.82,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,正常是多正常 教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.53,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.87,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,比起這個 合宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:44.50,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊對 合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.79,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,藉口 藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.67,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.59,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.30,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪禮露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.97,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,讓合宿什麼的都順利舉行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.14,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.57,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.91,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那麼重啟「給姐姐禮物的作戰大會」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.62,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,欸 不要不要 我要睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.83,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.92,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,嗯 準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.04,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.75,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,啊 風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.88,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.17,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,欸 突然有急事抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:39.18,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽不得不出門一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.05,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.72,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,茉莉和我們家的店鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.97,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,要去參加一個稍微有點遠的集市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.35,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,有點遠 在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.35,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,{\an8}東西放哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.10,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,嗯 在哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.23,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,記得是西邊 對西邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.78,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,我來接你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.20,main-CN,Mari,0,0,0,,流 風 借用一下爸爸媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.99,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,現在就來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.29,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,總之就在西邊 後天晚上就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.75,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸 後天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:18.01,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那個 我也有事打算出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.92,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.68,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,風也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.51,main-CN,Mom,0,0,0,,門鎖就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.09,main-CN,Dad,0,0,0,,{\an8}西邊 對 西邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,魔法 好強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.35,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,挺順利的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.04,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.42,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.30,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.59,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,之前看到它們感覺很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.80,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,也給姐姐一個用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.01,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.81,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,因為兩個是一組的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.60,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.81,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.19,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我會珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,送出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.04,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪禮露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.83,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,帕姆帕姆力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.43,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,今天也很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.73,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,已經出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.03,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.49,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.16,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.20,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,心情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.50,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,就這麼期待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.59,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,要選擇哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.43,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸 又是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.68,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,下一個 露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.10,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.93,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.06,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.52,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.53,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.48,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.36,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,哼 抱歉我也贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.49,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,表情太好猜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.91,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,這次一定要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.29,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,每次都有你們兩個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.13,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,這裡可是在列車上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.88,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.21,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.18,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.81,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.19,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,比想像中的還要好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.32,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.07,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,裡面也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.03,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我去裡面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.33,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好像可以玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.43,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,嗯 很好 就用來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.72,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.64,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,真虧你能租到這麼好的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.90,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.78,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,這個呀 說起來很便宜的 對吧社長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.03,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,配有私人海灘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.78,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,比起周邊的價格要低一半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.49,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,原本這是打算賣掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:18.16,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,結果賣不出去 只能出租了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.79,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,總之 是撿到寶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.58,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,我在別的地方住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.13,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,這邊就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.00,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,不要讓附近的居民困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.96,main-CN,All,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:30.97,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.10,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,附近什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:39.43,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那個 所以合宿到底要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.77,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸 是探險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.52,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不是先從選房間開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.77,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,這些都靠後 首先是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.53,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.07,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,為什麼 有泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.20,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,說是從事務所裡帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,真的可以游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.37,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,對 對啊 我們明明是為了練習而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.83,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,欸 夏天 大海 還有私人沙灘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.63,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,肯定是來游泳的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.88,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,游
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:09.76,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.17,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:12.55,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.18,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,行啦 露露也來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.68,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.71,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,我們也變得熱鬧起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.38,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,最初明明只有兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.34,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不還有社長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.97,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.10,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,但是有這麼好的兩位加入 真的太幸運啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.89,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,你說 這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.15,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,就能稱霸演藝圈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.15,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.11,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,嘿喲 嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.37,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,接下來 嘴唇開聲練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.37,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,像是用嘆氣一樣的感覺 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.59,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,接下來 哼唱訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.72,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.48,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,明明剛玩過後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.73,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,為什麼還能那麼有勁跳舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.69,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,因為是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.11,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,偶像所必要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.28,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子會全力以赴都做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:06.21,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,塔子姐 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.96,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,露露和莉莉也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.00,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,記住剛剛的舞步就是今天的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.17,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.05,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,能 能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.30,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,能的 世奈你要給點意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.35,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,也就 循環三百次就能記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.52,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,三百次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.39,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,記不住的話可是沒有晚餐吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.60,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,偶像好像很辛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.32,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,加 加油吧 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.20,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,把這些給兩人送過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:40.99,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.58,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.84,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,動不了了 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.01,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,多練幾次就能習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.30,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 卡八匹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.68,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,稍微休息會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.26,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.77,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.56,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,說起來 塔子姐和世奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,是從什麼時候開始當偶像的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.65,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,去年春天 塔子她突然說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.15,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.28,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,雖然做了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.33,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,但並不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.91,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,然後你們兩位就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:26.99,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.54,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子她也很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.42,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,有了你們兩位 夢想就有可能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.38,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:34.79,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:38.59,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,以偶像的身份獲得成功 驚艷大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.17,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,這就是塔子的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.05,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,為此還成立了間公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:46.35,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,從以前開始她就如此膽大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:49.93,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,兩位的關係非常好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.60,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,只是朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.06,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,讓我看看曾經的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.77,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不要 好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.94,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我把飲料拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.99,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.99,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8}我要看我要看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:04.49,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,還有 我也想看照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.33,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.91,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.96,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,很有精神呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.38,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,好啦 休息結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.46,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,剛剛學的來複習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.77,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,有拍攝到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.18,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,直播要說點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.85,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.81,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊 有觀眾進來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.65,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,晚上好 這裡是再次閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.24,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,這是第一次以直播形式和大家面對面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.82,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,好了 大家都來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.45,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,大家好 我是世奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.20,main-CN,Lilly,0,0,0,,晚上好 我是莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.70,main-CN,Lulu,0,0,0,,嚕嚕嚕 我是露露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.33,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嚕嚕嚕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.96,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,用力過猛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.04,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.38,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,最後我是塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.71,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 評論來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.17,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,問我們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.38,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,合宿用的獨棟小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.72,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.68,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.60,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,耶 耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:13.77,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,那個 有什麼話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.94,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,話題 話題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.40,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,露露有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.65,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.41,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.37,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.32,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.33,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,大家明明在直播之前還聊個不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.29,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.04,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊 越來越多人加入直播間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.01,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.88,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,評論來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.13,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,「我看了地獄問答」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 實際上很多人都看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,「已經成為你們的粉絲啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:54.93,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.94,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.02,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,都在計算中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,只要粉絲增加 勝算就在我們這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.32,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}莉莉好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.28,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,啊 有人說喜歡莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.91,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.87,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,我是莉莉的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.99,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,哇 好多人來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:16.12,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,很好很好 大家有什麼想問的儘管問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.71,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}困擾的莉莉醬好可愛！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.75,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}有什麼值得推薦的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.75,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,等會太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:21.67,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}我就是莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.92,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}有尊敬的偶像之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:23.96,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}我就是莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.63,main-CN,Idol Fan,0,0,0,,{\an8}莉莉醬休息日一般你做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.55,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊不是 我應付不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.88,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,等會 慢點 請大家一個個提問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.64,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.68,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,大家好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.27,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,啊 又有評論來了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.65,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,雖然很累但是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.94,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,觀看直播人數已經超過三千了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.03,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,完全應付不過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.45,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.95,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我們兩個人的時候根本沒有這麼大反響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.12,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,多虧了莉莉和露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.45,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.83,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:03.13,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,感謝兩位能夠加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.47,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,但是 我可不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.68,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,好 明天繼續槓槓地練習
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.14,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,今天就睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.30,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,槓槓？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.51,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,啊 又興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.35,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,請手下留情的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.49,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.60,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,明明你一個人能去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.14,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,可是 我怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你來自哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.62,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.29,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,等會我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.87,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,紅豆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.16,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是去豌豆那裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.00,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.96,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,早安 睡得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:08.75,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.01,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.88,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,就剩下莉莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:19.85,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,那孩子 絕對是那種早上起不來的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:20.89,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.10,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我去接她下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:30.36,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.99,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.99,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,已經天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.25,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.58,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,紅豆他們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.79,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.42,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是的 其它的房間我也去看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.42,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,看起來哪裡都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.93,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:19:58.64,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.18,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,會不會出去了呢 比如海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.44,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,啊 啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.06,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,塔子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,門打不開 明明沒有鎖門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.45,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,欸 你還沒睡醒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.95,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,是真的啊 你來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.41,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.95,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,有其它的出入口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.96,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.00,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,窗戶也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.46,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.09,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.55,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,塔 塔子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.47,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我給社長打電話試試
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.06,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.60,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,社長 緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.85,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉突然不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.23,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,難道不是外出散步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.44,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:58.74,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我們幾個現在也出不去屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.62,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,喂 聲音…聽得…見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.87,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.87,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,把電視的聲音關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.87,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.21,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,大笑的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.38,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,總之那些奇怪的聲音吵死了 我根本聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.59,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,電視 不是什麼…你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.68,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,欸 喂 喂 塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.43,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,社長 社長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.94,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.82,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,沒信號了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:41.82,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:44.57,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:01.30,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.49,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事啊

